messages.messageBody:
We have a set of felt people with lots of felt hair and felt clothes, to play with on a piece of felt-covered wood.

This was made for us by a friend. She went all out on the clothes, sewing or gluing on beads, lace, etc.

Mary Ellen

messages.messageBody:
Here's a site I found that I have used some. I want to do the magnetic ones
for all of my neices (5) but I'm slightly dreading the work of it :) There
are pages and pages different ethnic ones, wheelchairs, themes, tons of
stuff. They're kinda cutesy.

http://www.makingfriends.com

Katie
